value.0: If you have proof that you have defeated an enemy, let me know and i will compensate you accordingly and you will help to bring glory to our faction. I can also turn an ear you have collected into a trophy. You won't be able to cash it in later, but you will be able to show off your kills to everyone else.
Alright, which ear do you want me to make into a trophy?
Are you sure you want to turn this ear into a trophy? Once it has become a trophy you will no longer be able to trade it to me.
Very well, lets see what you've got
